<BLOCKQUOTE><FONT COLOR="#CC9933"><FONT SIZE=+1>Dreyfus has career opportunities
available in both business and technical areas. We offer a competitive
compensation package, full benefits, and ample opportunity for career growth.
For prompt, confidential consideration, you may send your resume to Human
Resources Department, The Dreyfus Corporation, 200 Park Avenue, New York,
NY 10166 or submit your resume online.&nbsp;</FONT></FONT>&nbsp;

<P><FONT COLOR="#CC9933"><FONT SIZE=+1>Dreyfus is an Equal Opportunity/Affirmative
Action Employer.&nbsp;</FONT></FONT></BLOCKQUOTE>

